Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:05.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(404,0)\pos(351,359)}Munich\N(Germany)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would certainly like to enjoy a round of golf next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please go easy on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We look forward to your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What curious people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our business negotiations ran\Na little longer than expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Iwai, from the Munich branch of Kadofuku AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lunge, from the German BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:00:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thank you and a bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and another for this gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding Yamamoto, the person\Nyou wanted to see, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on a business trip to the Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's scheduled to return tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do you know of Mr. Schuwald, the\Nhead of the great financial group?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he came out of retirement and\Nstarted economic activities again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the companies in Germany that are\Naffiliated with him have picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese trading firms are all busy\Nmaking deals with Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you laugh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, Yamamoto can't help you today, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he and I both know Mr. Kenzou Tenma equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still investigating him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I haven't closed the case yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 was really surprised when Mr. Tehma \N was identified as a suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really that unexpected?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was beyond unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 can't believe he killed someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to tell you the truth, I didn't\Nthink he'd do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we only went out drinking two\Nor three times three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he wasn't a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say he's not a bad person...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,does that make him a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good person...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, he was more...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't the type who likes to stand out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyone who doesn't like \N to stand out is a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's more like he didn't seem the\Nuncivil type, is what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:25.39,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(317,0)\pos(358,345)}A Nameless Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese don't usually wear things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese are skilled with chopsticks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called because I heard you're in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where I'm living now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My child... was born, and he's perfectly healthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though a lot has happened, \N I still want you to see my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, are you free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I should be free after six.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where shall we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Marienplatz...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good with chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although lately, there have been many foreigners\Nwho use chopsticks better than the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Dr. Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the perspective of someone in the same\Nbusiness, what kind of person was Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't too unsociable...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he was indecisive at times...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turns into a completely different\Nperson when he holds a scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called him a genius surgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that was definitely not an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about his parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't want to talk much about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he did say that both his father and\Nhis older brother are doctors...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess he had no choice \N but to become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he didn't return to Japan even once\Nafter he became a doctor in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:07:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His parents didn't come to \N Germany during that incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they didn't seem interested\Nin proving their son's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess his family isn't all that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 received a call from Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did arrive in Munich from Prague, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems he has to meet with a client right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he did say that he'll be coming to\Nthe restaurant we're heading to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The restaurant...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with us, Inspector Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't know when we'll\Nbe needing your help again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess his family isn't all that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 am...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:40.71,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.82,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx96.25\fscy97.5\org(476,166)\frz349.236\pos(359,169)}KARAOKE PUB
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.82,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(356,310)\frz353.326}Ooedo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:45.50,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:52.05,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Pleiades!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice going, Iwai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Would you like to sing one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the next song is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:17.28,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,Love letter from Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.70,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were here with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were here with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:27.57,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a wonderful trip it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:31.36,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,Love letter from Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blend into Japanese society...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ask for help here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a place to go home to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry for being late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you, Yamamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Inspector Lunge. I told you\Nabout him over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yamamoto, from the Munich branch of Kadofuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How were negotiations with Mr.\NKohout in the Czech Republic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that Schuwald's right-hand man,\Nthat blond-haired boy, was asking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because getting on Schuwald's\Nsecretary's good side...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the best way of getting a good\Ncontract from Schuwald himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to go through lots of used bookstores in Prague...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I finally found a copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so this is that picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cover has fallen off, and it's \N in pretty bad shape, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll look fine once we wrap it up nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I have a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in Czech...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, next is my song!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, what are you looking \N up in that dictionary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Czech words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Czech?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have something to \N do with your investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're looking, up things that have\N nothing to do with your investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a passage from a picture book, \N and liked the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanted to know what the passage said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inspector reading a picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Look, at me! Look at me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The monster inside me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"has grown this big!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Johan has finally gotten around to\Nmanipulating that large financial group!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hearing stories of Johan from\Nyou for a while now, Dr. Gillen, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Johan guy is a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've killed many people myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's become something I've always\Nwanted to be, but couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Johan is my hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's something else I want to talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were Johan, what would you do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd kill his current parents, the Lieberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'd have gotten bored with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Liebert!  Mr. Liebert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A psychoanalyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from us, Dr. Reichwein?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of wasting your\Ntime with the whole back-story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you something about\Nyour adopted son, Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan?  Adopted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our real son, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use trying to play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The grave of your real son is in Bruntal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took advantage of the \N town hall's files burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and turned in another birth certificate\Nas if your child were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:13:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 didn't come here to threaten you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a collected report on Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain person has collected all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came here once trying to sell us insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a former detective, Richard Braun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A former detective...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please read.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story begins in 1986...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when a high official of the East was exiled to the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he after money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't care about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did he attach himself to this wealthy man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also did it when you were little, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You find a line of ants...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you take that line of ants...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe such a frightening story...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you don't want to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost your son at an early age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, even though you weren't\Nblessed with another child...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a child who was about the same\Nage as your son appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he even had money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave you a wonderful house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave you a beautiful garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he gave you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand very well that \N you want to believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's written here is the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan... is a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is a kind boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and very skillful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our reason for living!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lived with him for nearly five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's all you can say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of him, my friend Richard is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now, a man named Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is trying to do something that can't be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like the middle-aged couples written about in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like those who raised Johan as an adopted son...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave here!  Leave with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small apples are ripening on our apple tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next year, we'll get bigger ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to be killed by a Japanese man soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan said that to the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think he meant by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for the record, he doesn't have a death wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what did he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes are always thinking of complicated things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can tell you this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the world was burnt to\Nthe ground in a nuclear war...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'd still survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's saying that we can't do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that everything we've done\Nhas been a fruitless effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even help Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Reichwein...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor have we found Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even stop him from killing Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has been a futile effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Reichwein, let's calm down and think it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mess up the line of ants, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even ants have souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only option now is to risk my\Nlife by fighting in close combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell him everything to his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that great mogul, Schuwald!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add another fifty chairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they keep coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Mr. Schuwald's \N donation ceremony tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The higher-ups all want to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time Mr. Schuwald makes\Na move, it becomes a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The library will be closing shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The library will be closing shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Czech dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.  This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed a Czech picture bookr but\NI don't understand anything it says...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend suddenly fainted \N after reading this picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought that maybe it had something\Nto do with what's written in the book...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your friend better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Once upon a time, in a far away land..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"there was a monster without a name."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:22:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The monster wanted a name so\Nbadly that he couldn't stand it."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So the monster decided to go on a journey."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange book...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We re closing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're closed tomorrow because of the ceremony.
