Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(188,474)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(193,23)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.40,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(188,474)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(191,20)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:25.94,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(190,474)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:34.36,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(189,471)}Make it home to your land of purity
